txt.en: Defeat many Bearers of Blight in Skirmishes. \nThis deed will only be advanced by Lieutenants that do not appear grey to your character, they must be around the same level as you are.
Defeat Bearers of Blight in Skirmishes
The uruk Bearers of Blight are weaponsmasters skilled with poisons and disease...they are a threat which must be eliminated.
